data.description: Welcome to this highly sought-after home in the Arcadia Ridge community, nestled in the vibrant far west side of San Antonio. Situated amidst an array of retail stores and popular restaurants, this spacious residence spans an impressive 3,276 square feet, featuring an expansive open floor plan that bathes the interior in natural light. The generous, well-appointed kitchen boasts ample storage and counter space, complemented by a convenient double oven. Your serene master suite awaits downstairs, complete with separate his and her closets. Upstairs, discover a versatile second living area, perfect for media or gaming, and easy access to the attic, providing even more storage space. Assumable Loan Rate at 2.750%
